data.description: Welcome to 908 James Road, your move-in-ready oasis nestled in a serene and inviting neighborhood. This charming home boasts 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, all updated to provide modern comfort and convenience. Situated on a spacious .22-acre lot, you'll have plenty of room to stretch out and enjoy the outdoors. Step inside to discover a beautifully maintained interior, meticulously cleaned and waiting for you to make it your own. Whether you're entertaining guests in the open living spaces or enjoying a quiet evening in the cozy bedrooms, this home offers the perfect blend of functionality and comfort. Outside, you'll find a tranquil retreat awaiting your enjoyment. From relaxing on the deck to exploring the lush surroundings, there's no shortage of opportunities to unwind and recharge. HOA maintains yard maintenance. Don't miss your chance to call 908 James Road home. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and convenience of this wonderful property for yourself!
